<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-11540] Unable to disable ProducerCache by setting cacheSize=&quot;-1&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-11540</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is not possible to disable ProducerCache for camel-rabbitmq, camel-netty4, camel-netty and camel-jms producers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, while trying to turn off activemq ProducerCache like:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;wireTap uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;activemq:foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt; cacheSize=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;-1&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;results in error :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;java.util.concurrent.RejectedExecutionException
    at org.apache.camel.component.jms.JmsProducer.process(JmsProducer.java:144)&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
