                            <comment id="16084563" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 12 Jul 2017 19:41:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user saravanakumar1987 opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/pull/1821&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/pull/1821&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-11540&quot; title=&quot;Unable to disable ProducerCache by setting cacheSize=&amp;quot;-1&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CAMEL-11540&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CAMEL-11540&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Fixed issue with turning off ProducerCache&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    ConcurrentLinkedHashMap attempts to evict entries when the max capacity is zero, eventually the service is stopped. This results in camel-netty, camel-netty4, activemq and rabitmwq producers unable to disable ProducerCache.&lt;/p&gt;

